{
  "id": "RAW_3daa36",
  "title": "从“知识仓鼠”到 AI 共创：小七姐重定义 AI 时代的知识管理新范式（上） ",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzE5OTE0NjIwNw==&mid=2247483914&idx=1&sn=d6b3600714a76653984a4ab3d1aaa5a8",
  "date": "2025-09-15 11:00:00",
  "author": "43 Talks",
  "siteName": "43 Talks",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=37232de2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FTDgwnHxZMLSfe1dUWOnJl2iaZTKT5ReIyBJib5fu5miaI1AnoYWiahMQWMU6H1G9QOXsXJV1Aue9ibxahWrgmIX7uAw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:inline !important;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkriuw41pw0\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qai41\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mfkrj7kh1n1l\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">信息爆炸时代，我们是否正陷入一场“知识囤积”的内耗？</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa1kwf\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\">我们像仓鼠一样，将两颊塞满信息，收藏、剪贴、建立无数文件夹和标签，但真正能被灵活调用的知识，却只占冰山一角。当AI浪潮来袭，这种传统的知识管理模式正面临彻底的颠覆。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa1ovs\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在近期由&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">43 College</span>与<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">易论AI</span>联合发起的</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(57, 86, 218);\">43 Talks</span></span><span leaf=\"\">第三期线下思辨沙龙“重构与重塑AI浪潮下的知识、商业与价值新秩序”中，第一位分享嘉宾43 Consulting CEO<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 169, 0);font-weight: bold;\">小七姐</span>拨开迷雾，结合自身经历为大家分享了一条从</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">“知识囤积者”转型“AI共创者”</span></span><span leaf=\"\">的实用路径，共同探讨了</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(57, 86, 218);\">AI时代知识管理的三个核心问题：</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qajt3\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">第一，AI时代前，我们的知识管理困境是什么？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa197z\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">第二，什么是“上下文共创”新范式？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qacsj\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">第三，如何构建与AI共生的知识管理闭环？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><em mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa1wz0\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">小七姐，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">43 Consulting（43咨询）创始人、43 College 联合创始人，著有《智能体设计指南</span></span><strong style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:0px;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;margin-right:0px;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;visibility: visible;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">——</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">成为提示词高手和 AI Agent 设计师》，参与共创 AI 开源社区《通往 AGI 之路》。其主要研究方向包括提示词工程、智能体设计及企业 AI 应用落地。</span></span></em></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 0px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100000234\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4875\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/TDgwnHxZMLSfe1dUWOnJl2iaZTKT5ReIyab9UYpw3PuqsibbjmPC63j7F6p4gX7m6W166TUJRA2cZfws2d0UZ56Q/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"321\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"282\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2ab960d1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FTDgwnHxZMLSfe1dUWOnJl2iaZTKT5ReIyab9UYpw3PuqsibbjmPC63j7F6p4gX7m6W166TUJRA2cZfws2d0UZ56Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-data-temp-type=\"divider\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mfaxpwc21p0u\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;width: 677px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;width: 59px;height: 9px;text-align: justify;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;line-height: 1.6em;\"><img style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;vertical-align: bottom;display: block;background-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 59px !important;\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.15254237288135594\" data-w=\"118\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=641f00e2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FIBThicqc6MwtuO6o3dHnibpaBo5ribFbdESRB8UD3eEhze3xDBPZF7unyolgF95ZOnahduVibaLflJwMlSXLbNC3Tg%2F640%3Ftp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D0\"></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><strong mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qangy\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mfkrke5eouu\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrke4u1jsp\"><span leaf=\"\">传</span></span></span><span mpa-font-style=\"mfkrke4u1cbj\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;\">统</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;\">知</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;\">识管理</span></span></span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrke4u5ij\"><span leaf=\"\">的困境：从DIKW到信息仓库</span></span></span></strong></h2>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa1gfj\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">小七姐的分享从一个直击痛点的拷问开始：“我们真正能够调用出来的知识，占我们已经囤积的知识的百分之几？”她用一个生动的比喻描绘了大多数知识管理爱好者的现状</span><strong style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:0px;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;margin-right:0px;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;visibility: visible;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">——</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(57, 86, 218);\">“知识仓鼠”。</span></span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa1z5t\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\">“仓鼠的两颊塞的鼓鼓的，我们大量的去收藏剪贴，然后建立各种各样、形形色色、五颜六色的文件夹和各种各样的tag。但实际上我们能够调用的灵活调用的这种知识和智慧，跟我们海量的囤积比起来，比例可能是非常低的。”</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa1wah\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">她回顾了AI时代前知识管理的两大经典框架，第一个是</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(57, 86, 218);\">DIKW模型</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，它将人与知识的关系划分为四个层级：</span></span></p>\n  <ol class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" start=\"1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa1sdp\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">数据 (Data)：</span></span><span leaf=\"\">客观记录的原始符号。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa21dr\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">信息 (Information)</span></span><span leaf=\"\">：经过主观解读、赋予意义的数据。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa1arp\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">知识 (Knowledge)：</span></span><span leaf=\"\">能够被调用和运用来解决问题的结构化信息。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa13pl\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">智慧 (Wisdom)：</span></span><span leaf=\"\">内化于心、形成远见和综合判断能力的顶层认知。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100000192\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.47129629629629627\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/TDgwnHxZMLStkEXtTRIemwk4se3J4vvFbwnCPgsfOPOaaKc7CNmrn8IXzCSSZ5rtKJFul5ggXr5lBnJ5ib96vlg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1080\" data-cropy1=\"54.18685121107266\" data-cropy2=\"562.4221453287197\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"272\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=233812a2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FTDgwnHxZMLSfe1dUWOnJl2iaZTKT5ReIyxRC6KWsd00yyLF6icMCaSt0J4HNuMqkWu6B9sfiah7zcDpFbVG1QQsGA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qasx4\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">第二个是广为人知的</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(57, 86, 218);\">PARA方法，</span></span><span leaf=\"\">一种信息组织原则，它建议我们将所有信息归入四个顶级分类：</span></span></p>\n  <ol class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" start=\"1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa9p0\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">项目 (Projects)：</span></span><span leaf=\"\">有明确目标和截止日期的任务。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qajkx\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">领域 (Areas)：</span></span><span leaf=\"\">需要长期关注和维护的责任范围。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa1euh\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">资源 (Resources)：</span></span><span leaf=\"\">个人感兴趣的、可供未来参考的资料。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa1qnw\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">归档 (Archives)：</span></span><span leaf=\"\">已完成或不再活跃的项目和资料。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100000193\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4527777777777778\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/TDgwnHxZMLStkEXtTRIemwk4se3J4vvFZTwVbGLXbppOYvibRYMuO10LDfian6rAdGr5icyLueFp9A9ibibdMHhfdXQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1080\" data-cropy1=\"61.66089965397923\" data-cropy2=\"549.3425605536331\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"262\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d2edfbc6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FTDgwnHxZMLSfe1dUWOnJl2iaZTKT5ReIyTy5eSibJiaicuHQvMAEzRWDmUzegNEccibvEruZvHVerzDjJhHCWyKBhOA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa19zo\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\">小七姐肯定了这些方法的价值：“毋庸置疑，我认为它们都是非常系统性的，能够帮我们构建一种最基本的信息管理的思路。”然而，她也一针见血地指出了这些传统方法论中凸显的问题：</span></p>\n  <ol class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" start=\"1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa1rof\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">重“存”轻“用”：</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qafks\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\">我们绝大部分精力被消耗在如何分类、如何存储信息上，而对于“知识如何用好”的探讨和实践，却始终是少数人的专利。</span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa12we\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\">“我们可以看到很多优秀的知识管理者，就知识用的非常好的人大概率他都是一个非常好的知识型的IP……但实际上他们总是极少数的。”</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <ol class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" start=\"2\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qaf8n\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">理想与现实的鸿沟：</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa24hs\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\">对于不具备编程思维的广大文科工作者和创作者而言，像处理数据库一样管理自己的文本和思想，本身就存在巨大的认知和操作门槛。</span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa22e5\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\">“我们想象中的那个理想的，我们自己想象中我们是在建这个知识体系，但实际上我们最终建出来其实就是一个信息仓库。”</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <ol class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" start=\"3\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa3v0\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">人适应工具的本末倒置：</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa1w7\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\">最核心的问题在于，“之前我们做的方法其实是人去适应这些方法和工具，而不是让工具来适应人的需求。”我们花费大量时间学习和遵从复杂的规则，却离知识应用的初衷越来越远。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100000195\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5277777777777778\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/TDgwnHxZMLStkEXtTRIemwk4se3J4vvFjGGuNRlrW4HRMlmXTFu30X5sbliaBbnLCxM1dApDJTYwTB6kibibfhvCw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1080\" data-cropy2=\"569.8961937716263\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"305\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c95b3b19&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FTDgwnHxZMLSfe1dUWOnJl2iaZTKT5ReIy526Q6RGOtJnRFpuZQE6icicd1icI9XNMNiav67VgHgdP2Otw9ibp7Sm1kBA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-data-temp-type=\"divider\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mfaxpwc21p0u\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-ta