al;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa2zx\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mfkrklm3u36\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrkllp1dfa\"><span leaf=\"\">AI</span></span></span></strong><span mpa-font-style=\"mfkrkllpson\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;\">时代的知识管理新</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;\">范式</span></span></strong></span><strong><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 86, 218);font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrkllp1rrm\"><span leaf=\"\">：上下文共创</span></span></span></strong></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa232i\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\">AI的到来，如同一股巨浪，彻底冲击了这套以“存储”为核心的旧范式。小七姐大胆地抛出了她的核心观点，为AI时代的知识管理重新下了定义：</span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qazj8\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\">“我认为现在AI时代的知识管理就变成了一个上下文共创的一种新范式。”</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <h3 style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa24ry\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(57, 86, 218);\">什么是“上下文”？</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qacdc\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\">它不再仅仅是你精心编写、发给AI的那一段结构化提示词。而是一种更广阔、更动态的概念：你上传的资料、你写好的文档、你与AI的每一次对话记录，甚至AI返回给你的长篇大论，都共同构成了你与AI协作的“共同语言”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><strong mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qaflf\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\">管理的重心，从“信息存储”决定性地转向了“上下文管理”。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100000240\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.52265625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/TDgwnHxZMLSfe1dUWOnJl2iaZTKT5ReIy6icEIic0CjTySSzO6yyf71KAMY8yic6GwWwUdYGhjT76428pjDFANjK7w/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1280\" data-cropy2=\"668.7889273356402\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"302\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=48579105&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FTDgwnHxZMLSfe1dUWOnJl2iaZTKT5ReIyGfG0VwI6ASaBaIM9FCMTha87qbc5N6ibvhsntYo1ZCsbLicQt5vqCwPA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <h4 style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa4j4\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(57, 86, 218);\">解放人力：专注于提问与判断</span></span></strong></h4>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qappe\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\">这种新范式的核心价值，在于它将人类从繁琐、重复的信息整理和初级加工中解放出来。那么，被解放出来的时间和精力应该用在何处？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><strong mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qaeds\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\">“用来专注于提出好问题和做出好判断，这两件事情变得至关重要。”</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qale\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\">小七姐还分享了她个人的沉浸式体验：在被工作、爱好和生活三重压力包围时，AI的介入让她感受到了前所未有的自由。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa197f\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\">当AI能够深度理解你的上下文，成为一个高效的共创伙伴时，人的核心角色便升维为两件事：提出真正有洞察力的问题，和做出基于智慧和价值观的精准判断。</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100000229\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.51875\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/TDgwnHxZMLSfe1dUWOnJl2iaZTKT5ReIycD7jPESSibINUlMAZECvf3oWRxt2zeAyUXmxnpSta78Ria8UEFeN0kiaQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1280\" data-cropy2=\"664.3598615916956\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"300\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4148daa8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FTDgwnHxZMLSfe1dUWOnJl2iaZTKT5ReIyOF14kTFmcQPs37jlztBx1OMZeaYceHIM4EPfKvyWZXdb4zpmVA9lTg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa1m0w\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这正是AI时代知识管理带来的<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">“自由爽”</span></span><strong style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:0px;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;margin-right:0px;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;visibility: visible;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">——</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">将重复性脑力劳动外包给AI，把我们自己最宝贵的注意力，聚焦在最有价值的创造性思考上。</span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mfawrpc5pzd\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <div data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;width: 677px;\">\n    <div data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;\">\n     <p data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;width: 35px;height: 32px;text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;line-height: 1.6em;\"><img style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;vertical-align: bottom;background-color: transparent;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 34.9922px !important;\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9130434782608695\" data-w=\"138\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e2b4e433&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fib55wokfSaZMaJHickoB3S3VQI8K17yjyb97bsQVt2Ny8L6xEXQumFTsDgPbD2QsgYcZbtPZ3tmHBXl3NXUvWsPA%2F640%3Ftp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D8\"></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa1i8y\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\">深入了解了“上下文共创”的颠覆性理念，我们该如何将其付诸实践？如何构建一个让知识在与AI的互动中持续增值的“<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">共创闭环”</span>？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qa6nk\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\">又该如何像小七姐一样，灵活运用上下文与AI共创一篇逻辑严密、风格独特的深度稿件？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\"><strong mpa-font-style=\"mfkrk4qawtc\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在下篇分享中，我们将深入拆解小七姐的“上下文共创闭环”四步法，并完整复盘她那场惊艳的“AI辅助演讲稿生成”实战案例。敬请期待！</span></strong></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章深度剖析了 AI 时代下知识管理的传统困境，并提出了以“上下文共创”为核心的新范式，强调人类应专注于提出好问题和做出好判断。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章深度剖析了 AI 时代下知识管理的传统困境，并提出了以“上下文共创”为核心的新范式，强调人类应专注于提出好问题和做出好判断。",
  "summary": "本文由 43 Consulting CEO 小七姐分享，深入探讨了 AI 时代前知识管理的困境，指出传统 DIKW 模型和 PARA 方法论虽然系统，但普遍存在重“存”轻“用”、理想与现实脱节、以及人适应工具的本末倒置问题，导致多数人沦为“知识仓鼠”。面对 AI 浪潮，文章提出“上下文共创”作为知识管理的新范式，将管理的重心从“信息存储”转向“上下文管理”，即所有与 AI 的互动和资料都构成动态的“共同语言”。这种新范式旨在解放人类从繁琐的信息整理中，使我们能将精力聚焦于提出有洞察力的问题和做出基于智慧的判断，从而实现知识的持续增值和个人生产力的升维。文章作为上篇，为读者描绘了 AI 时代知识管理变革的宏大图景，并预告下篇将深入拆解具体实践方法。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "传统知识管理模式重“存”轻“用”，导致效率低下。",
      "explanation": "DIKW 和 PARA 等传统方法论虽系统，但促使人们将大量精力消耗在信息分类和存储上，实际可灵活调用的知识比例极低，形成“知识仓鼠”现象。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 时代知识管理重心转向“上下文共创”新范式。",
      "explanation": "AI 的介入将知识管理从静态的信息存储转变为动态的“上下文管理”，即所有上传资料和与 AI 的对话共同构建协作语境，实现人机共创。"
    },
    {
      "point": "人类在 AI 时代的核心价值在于提出好问题和做出好判断。",
      "explanation": "AI 接管重复性信息加工，解放人类精力，使其专注于更高层次的创造性思考、提问和基于智慧的判断，实现个人生产力的升维。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "我们真正能够调用出来的知识，占我们已经囤积的知识的百分之几？",
    "之前我们做的方法其实是人去适应这些方法和工具，而不是让工具来适应人的需求。",
    "我认为现在 AI 时代的知识管理就变成了一个上下文共创的一种新范式。",
    "管理的重心，从'信息存储'决定性地转向了'上下文管理'。",
    "用来专注于提出好问题和做出好判断，这两件事情变得至关重要。"
  ],
